high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the butter knife from the fridge.
Cut the tomato into pieces using the knife.
Put the butter knife in the fridge.
Then take the piece of tomato from the fridge.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the tomato into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go near the microwave.
Put the tomato into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of tomato into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to a fridge.
Take a butterknife out of the fridge.
Cut a tomato in the fridge using the butterknife.
Put the butterknife back in the fridge.
Pick up a tomato slice from the fridge.
Turn right and walk to a sink in front of you.
Put the tomato slice in the sink, rinse it out, and take it back out.
Step back a bit and focus on a microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed-up tomato slice in the microwave.
